{"about_the_game":"<strong>Nightmare Side</strong> originated as a horror radio show from <strong>Ardan Radio</strong>, running since 1997, and sharing real spooky stories from the citizens of <strong>Bandung City, Indonesia</strong>. In this game, players will explore the radio office itself, which is famously haunted.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Don't Listen to Nightmare Side Alone&quot; Mechanic</h2>This tagline of the show is an actual mechanic in the game. The longer you listen to the show alone, the more danger you face.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Meticulously Recreated Real-Life Location</h2>The game takes place in the Ardan Radio office, recreated 1:1 compared to the real location in Bandung, Indonesia, offering an authentic spooky atmosphere.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Authentic Indonesian Lore based on Investigation</h2>Encounter authentic Indonesian lore discovered during our investigations and interviews, along with unsettling new discoveries.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Original Cast and Radio Show Episodes</h2>The game features Dimasta, the renowned presenter of the Nightmare Side show, and includes some of the actual episode recordings broadcasted in the game.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Lights Out","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2649780/0ada2268f1e0d0bbbe2794a54135202dea46f208.jpg"},{"name":"The True Runner","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2649780/5ff503ec3ce1a23d1e70586eec53cbc4dcc4f02d.jpg"},{"name":"The Ending Collector","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2649780/a957b1020ae873d36691d81bdba1f68cb31632c9.jpg"},{"name":"The Elevator Survivor","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2649780/7e125aa72d6a7407030ac3b76c1d5577599b0eb0.jpg"},{"name":"The Mediator","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2649780/bfc3b79eda58c0f17371d6118ba58d09e062f471.jpg"},{"name":"Ba